  <brief_title>Observational Study Concerning COVID-19 Infection in Transplanted Kidney, Pancreas or Pancreatic Islet Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Study to Assess the Health Status of Transplanted Patients (Kidney or Pancreas or Pancreatic Islet Transplantation) at Transplant Medicine Unit (MITRA) During the COVID-19 Pandemic</official_title>
