  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Collect informations on the health status of transplanted patients (kidney, kidney /
      pancreas, pancreas or pancreatic islet) during the COVID-19 pandemic. All informations will
      be collected by short questionnaire via phone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
